  "prompt": "What does my birth chart say about my future especially about my career and marriage?",
  "response": "To provide insights into your future regarding career and marriage based on your birth chart, I would need specific details such as your date of birth, time of birth, and place of birth. This information can be used to calculate the positions of the planets and the aspects they create, which can guide interpretations related to career and relationships.\n\nHowever, please note that astrology is a belief system and interpretations can vary widely among astrologers. Many also emphasize personal agency and the influence of choices and actions over astrological indicators.\n\nIf you would like to provide your birth details, I can give a general overview of how astrologers might analyze your chart for career and marriage insights.",
